name: Sai Blackbyrn

bio: Sai Blackbyrn, formally known as Sai C.N.G. Blackbyrn, is a leading figure in the coaching industry and CEO of Coach Foundation. Coming from a family of coaches, he is an entrepreneur and speaker known for helping coaches grow successful businesses online. He is also an author with multiple published works.
